name: Inazuma Eleven 1-2-3!! - Endou Mamoru Densetsu [3DS]
description:
Inazuma Eleven 1-2-3: The Legend of Endou Mamoru is a sports-arcade game developed by Level 5. It came out on 29-11-2012. It was published by Level-5.
You can play Inazuma Eleven 1-2-3: The Legend of Endou Mamoru on Nintendo 3DS.
